-- MOVES-Deloitte Corporate Finance names Thomas Sloop as managing director in Houston
-- 
-- Fri Sep 05, 2014 03:02AM EDT
-- None



Sept 5 (Reuters) - Broker dealer Deloitte Corporate Finance LLC said it appointed Thomas Sloop as managing director for its office in Houston.

Sloop will lead the development of the company's oil and gas investment banking practice. He previously worked with Pace Global Energy, a Siemens Corp business, where he led the midstream mergers and acquisitions advisory practice.